The paper deals with the study of constraint codes for permutations, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The constraints studied in the paper are also related to data structures (cs.DS) and combinatorics (cs.DM). The paper also discusses the capacity of these constraints, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and signal processing (cs.SI).
